overview.en: TNK is the main network token that runs the Turing network. It uses the staking mining economic model to ensure the security of the main network. Anyone can mortgage TNK as a super node for NPOS mining. At the same time, after the main network line, any data interaction between parallel chains needs to consume a very small value of TNK to motivate the collector.
overview.zh: TNK是运行图灵网络的主网token，用staking挖矿的经济模型来保证主网安全性，任何人都可以抵押TNK成为超级节点进行NPOS挖矿。同时在主网上线之后，在平行链之间进行任何数据的交互，需要消耗很小数值的TNK以激励收集人。
